part.content:
#cloud-config

# Required packages
packages:
  - autoconf
  - automake
  - make
  - gcc-c++
  - pcre-devel
  - zlib-devel
  - libmemcached-devel
  - libevent
  - libevent-devel
  - openssl-devel
  - git

# Commands to run
runcmd:
  - "git clone https://github.com/RedisLabs/memtier_benchmark && (cd memtier_benchmark; autoreconf -iv && ./configure && make install) && rm -rf memtier_benchmark"
